{{2021 United States Capitol attack}}
'''2021年美国国会大厦遭冲击事件'''（{{lang-en|2021 Storming of United States Capitol}}）是指2021年1月6日，時任[[美国|美国]][[美国总统|總統]][[唐納·川普|唐納·川普]]的支持者暴力闯入[[美国国会大厦|美国国会大厦]]的[[骚乱|骚乱]]事件。当天，2000至2500名<ref name="NPR2022-01-06">{{Cite news|title=Where the Jan. 6 insurrection investigation stands, one year later|language=en|work=[[全国公共广播电台|NPR]]|url=https://www.npr.org/2022/01/06/1070736018/jan-6-anniversary-investigation-cases-defendants-justice|quote=But the department estimates that between 2,000 and 2,500 people entered the Capitol on Jan. 6, 2021, which means investigators still have a long way to go to hold everyone to account.[但该部门估计，2021年1月6日有2,000至2,500人进入国会大厦，这意味着调查人员仍有很长的路要走，以追究所有人的责任。]|access-date=2022-01-09|archive-date=2022-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220106211933/https://www.npr.org/2022/01/06/1070736018/jan-6-anniversary-investigation-cases-defendants-justice|dead-url=no}}</ref>示威者在特朗普的号召下冲进了美国国会大厦，扰乱正在进行{{tsl|en|2021 United States Electoral College vote count|2021年美国国会选举计票|计票}}及认证[[2020年美國總統選舉|2020年美国总统选举结果]]以宣告[[乔·拜登|乔·拜登]]正式获胜的[[美國國會聯席會議|美國國會聯席會議]]<ref name="2021-01-11-ap-sinister" /><ref>{{cite news|url=https://apnews.com/article/congress-confirm-joe-biden-78104aea082995bbd7412a6e6cd13818|title=Pro-Trump mob storms US Capitol in bid to overturn election|date=2021-01-07|work=AP News|access-date=2021-07-03|archive-date=2021-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210729042556/https://apnews.com/article/congress-confirm-joe-biden-78104aea082995bbd7412a6e6cd13818|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{tsl|en|United States Capitol Complex|国会大厦建筑群}}被封锁，其中的立法者和工作人员被紧急疏散，之后被骚乱人群占领并破坏长达数个小时。一系列的冲突导致5人死亡，超过140人受伤<ref name="YsUXQ">{{Cite web |last=Evelyn |first=Kenya |date=2021-01-09 |title=Capitol attack: the five people who died |url=https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2021/jan/08/capitol-attack-police-officer-five-deaths |website=The Guardian |access-date=2021-03-28 |archive-date=2021-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113193359/https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2021/jan/08/capitol-attack-police-officer-five-deaths |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

