on: How a Trump mob halted American democracy |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/graphics/2021/politics/trump-insurrection-capitol/ |deadurl=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113010357/https://www.washingtonpost.com/graphics/2021/politics/trump-insurrection-capitol/ |archive-date=2021-01-13 |access-date=January 24, 2021 |quote=The attack, which some historians called the most severe assault on the Capitol since the British sacked the building in 1814 |newspaper=The Washington Post }}</ref>。
=== 疫情下的美國 ===
