==== 示威者闯入国会大厦 ====
美國國會參眾兩院在下午舉行聯席會議，認證選舉人團選出拜登為下一任美國總統，副總統彭斯主持會議。<ref name=美國之音2022617>{{cite news |title=证人：特朗普曾一再吁请彭斯推翻2020年选举结果 |url=https://www.voachinese.com/a/trump-repeatedly-implored-pence-to-upend-2020-election-outcome-witnesses-testify-20220616/6620825.html}}</ref>原本该流程在以往仅被当做是“走过场”，但由于部分共和党人此前表示将阻挠这一过程，因此外界预料认证过程将出现波折。当联席会议开始认证[[亞利桑那州|亚利桑那州]]的选举结果时，来自亚利桑那州的众议员[[保羅·戈薩拉|保罗·戈萨拉]]以及来自[[德克萨斯州|得克萨斯州]]的参议员[[泰德·克鲁兹|泰德·克鲁兹]]提出反对动议，联席会议被迫暂停，国会两院各自退回到自己的议院展开限时两小时的自由辩论。<ref>{{Cite web|title=GOP lawmakers object to Arizona electors, launching futile bid to undo Biden's victory|url=https://www.politico.com/news/2021/01/06/gop-lawmakers-object-to-arizona-electors-455462|accessdate=2021-01-07|last=Forgey|first=Quint|work=[[政客_(媒体)|政客]]|language=en|archivedate=2021-01-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106212206/https://www.politico.com/news/2021/01/06/gop-lawmakers-object-to-arizona-electors-455462|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2021年1月6日下午2点15分左右开始，示威者<ref>{{Cite news|last1=Fandos|title=Pence and lawmakers evacuated as protesters storm the Capitol, halting Congress's counting of electoral votes.|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106201215/https://www.nytimes.com/live/2021/01/06/us/electoral-vote|archivedate=2021-01-06|issn=0362-4331|access-date=2021-01-06|url=https://www.nytimes.com/live/2021/01/06/us/electoral-vote|work=[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]|language=en-US|date=2021-01-06|first1=Nicholas|first5=Zolan|last5=Kanno-Youngs|first4=Glenn|last4=Thrush|first3=Eileen|last3=Sullivan|first2=Emily|last2=Cochrane|dead-url=no}}</ref>开始试图冲击国会大厦建筑群。包括副總統彭斯在內的<ref name=美國之音2022617/>部分建筑中的人員被疏散，一些暴力示威者冲破安保进入国会大厦。<ref name="McEvoy-Forbes" /><ref name=":1" /><!--有人在大廈外架起了執行死刑的{{link-en|絞架|Gallows}}、刺破國會外停泊的警車的輪胎並在其車窗留下「[[南希·佩洛西|佩洛西]]是[[撒旦|撒旦]]」的字句<ref name="Stunning" />。冲击国会大厦的行动多是在亲特朗普的极右翼社交媒体网站上组织，例如[[Gab|Gab]]和[[Parler|Parler]]，这些网站上的一些内容呼吁对国会实施暴力，平台还被作为[[匿名者Q|匿名者Q]]、[[驕傲男孩|驕傲男孩]]和其他边缘分子的招募中心长达数周。<ref>{{Cite news|last=Frenkel|first=Sheera|date=2021-01-06|title=The storming of Capitol Hill was organized on social media.|language=en-US|work=紐約時報|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/06/us/politics/protesters-storm-capitol-hill-building.html|access-date=2021-01-06|issn=0362-4331|archivedate=2021-01-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106220539/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/06/us/politics/protesters-storm-capitol-hill-building.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>-->在突破安全警戒线后，<ref>{{cite web|first1=Michael|last1=Balsamo|first2=Colleen|last2=Long|url=https://apnews.com/article/ap-electoral-college-congress-7af85d3c702e070464d7713c42cf254a|title=The Latest: Schumer says Jan. 6, 2021, will live in infamy|work=[[美聯社|美聯社]]|date=2020-01-06|accessdate=2021-01-07|archive-date=2021-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107023031/https://apnews.com/article/ap-electoral-college-congress-7af85d3c702e070464d7713c42cf254a|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/dc-md-va/2021/01/06/dc-protests-trump-rally-live-updates/|title=Woman dies after shooting in U.S. Capitol; D.C. National Guard activated after mob breaches building|work=華盛頓郵報|date=2021-01-06|accessdate=2021-01-06|archive-date=2021-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106194011/https://www.washingtonpost.com/dc-md-va/2021/01/06/dc-protests-trump-rally-live-updates/|dead-url=no}}</ref>大多数闯入者步行进入国会大厦，另有一部分人利用绳索和临时造出来的梯子进入大厦，有些人则打破窗户进入。<ref>{{cite web|first1=Harrison|last1=Smith|first2=Antonio|last2=Olivo|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/dc-md-va/2021/01/06/dc-protests-trump-rally-live-updates/#link-FPWYI3GZLFFBFORZYPBSQ7B76M|title=Rioters use ropes, makeshift ladders to invade Capitol|work=華盛頓郵報|date=2021-01-06|accessdate=2021-01-06|archive-date=2021-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106194011/https://www.washingtonpost.com/dc-md-va/2021/01/06/dc-protests-trump-rally-live-updates/#link-FPWYI3GZLFFBFORZYPBSQ7B76M|dead-url=no}}</ref>同时，不少示威者大喊众议院院长[[南希·佩洛西|南希·佩洛西]]和副总统[[迈克·彭斯|彭斯]]的名字，群眾更起哄吶喊“把[[迈克·彭斯|迈克·彭斯]]处以绞刑”（Hang Mike Pence）<ref>{{Cite web|title='Hang Mike Pence': Twitter stops phrase trending after Capitol riot|url=http://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2021/jan/10/hang-mike-pence-twitter-stops-phrase-trending-capitol-breach|accessdate=2021-01-13|date=2021-01-10|work=[[衛報|衛報]]|language=en|archivedate=2021-01-14|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114195832/https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2021/jan/10/hang-mike-pence-twitter-stops-phrase-trending-capitol-breach|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在暴动者闯入国会后，国会大厦建筑群的所有建筑都被封锁，不许进出。大楼内的人被要求躲在办公室并锁好门窗。在办公室外的人则被告知“寻找掩护”。<ref name=":52"/>执法人员开始在大楼内使用[[催泪瓦斯|催泪瓦斯]]后，國會告訴還在場內的議員、工作人員和記者戴上[[防毒面具|防-{}-毒面具]]。<ref name=":2" />數十人持槍與高舉{{link-en|南部聯盟軍旗的復興|Modern display of the Confederate battle flag|象徵白人優越的南部聯盟軍旗}}；參、眾議員輪流被安全撤離。<ref name=":3">{{Cite web|title=不斷更新／美總統認證爆衝突 川粉攻破國會1人中彈亡、華府宣布宵禁|url=https://udn.com/news/story/121687/5154248|accessdate=2021-01-07|author1=張文馨|author2=羅曉媛|author3=張筠|date=2021-01-07|format=|work=[[聯合新聞網|聯合新聞網]]|language=zh-hant|archivedate=2021-01-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106224742/https://udn.com/news/story/121687/5154248|dead-url=no}}</ref>据[[俄勒冈州|俄勒冈州]]参议员[[傑夫·默克利|傑夫·默克利]]称，一些工作人员成功地赶到议会厅，将数箱密封的选举人团选票解救出来避免被暴力示威者烧毁。<ref name="BBC-live" /><ref>{{cite web|first=Maureen|last=Chowdhury|url=https://www.cnn.com/politics/live-news/congress-electoral-college-vote-count-2021/h_54d83f1c965ed437e20ebda36839bd14|title=Lawmaker says staff were able to remove electoral ballots before rioters breached Senate floor|work=有線電視新聞網|date=2021-01-06|accessdate=2021-01-07|archive-date=2021-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106230313/https://www.cnn.com/politics/live-news/congress-electoral-college-vote-count-2021/h_54d83f1c965ed437e20ebda36839bd14|dead-url=no}}</ref>

