2021年1月6日下午2点31分，[[华盛顿哥伦比亚特区|華盛頓特區]]市长[[穆里尔·鲍泽|穆里尔·鲍泽]]下令从当晚6点开始实施[[宵禁|宵禁]]，持续至次日早上6时。<ref>{{Cite web|title=特朗普支持者衝進國會大廈與警方對峙 華盛頓即將宵禁|url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-55565454|accessdate=2021-01-07|date=2021-01-06|work=英國廣播公司新聞|language=zh-hant|archivedate=2021-01-07|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107071036/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-55565454|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=DC Mayor Issues 6 p.m. Curfew Following Protests Wednesday|url=https://baltimore.cbslocal.com/2021/01/06/dc-mayor-issues-6-p-m-curfew-following-protests-wednesday/|date=2021-01-06|last=|first=|language=en-US|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106203221/https://baltimore.cbslocal.com/2021/01/06/dc-mayor-issues-6-p-m-curfew-following-protests-wednesday/|archivedate=2021-01-06|access-date=2021-01-06|work=[[CBS_Baltimore|CBS Baltimore]]|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[弗吉尼亚州|弗吉尼亚州]]州长[[拉尔夫·诺森|拉尔夫·诺森]]也对邻近的[[亚历山德里亚_(弗吉尼亚州)|亚历山德里亚]]和[[北弗吉尼亚|北弗吉尼亚]]的[[阿靈頓縣_(維吉尼亞州)|阿靈頓縣]]发布了宵禁令。<ref>{{Cite web|title=The Latest: Armed police clear out rioters, Capitol complex 'secured'|url=https://www.wric.com/news/u-s-world/at-least-one-building-near-u-s-capitol-evacuated-due-to-the-unrest/|date=2021-01-06|language=en-US|access-date=2021-01-06|work=8News|archivedate=2021-01-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106233522/https://www.wric.com/news/u-s-world/at-least-one-building-near-u-s-capitol-evacuated-due-to-the-unrest/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.wfxrtv.com/news/regional-news/virginia-news/gov-northam-issues-state-of-emergency-issues-curfew-in-alexandria-arlington/|title=Gov. Northam issues State of Emergency, institutes curfew in Alexandria, Arlington|work=WFXR-TV|date=2020-01-06|accessdate=2021-01-07|archive-date=2021-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107025705/https://www.wfxrtv.com/news/regional-news/virginia-news/gov-northam-issues-state-of-emergency-issues-curfew-in-alexandria-arlington/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

弗吉尼亚州州长诺森派出了弗吉尼亚国民警卫队和200名弗吉尼亚州警支援华盛顿特区的执法工作。<ref name="Northam1">{{cite news|last1=Williamson|first1=Jeff|title=Gov. Northam sending Virginia National Guard and 200 state troopers to Washington, DC|url=https://www.wsls.com/news/virginia/2021/01/06/gov-northam-sending-virginia-national-guard-and-200-state-troopers-to-washington-dc/|work=WSLS|date=2021-01-06|language=en|access-date=2021-01-06|archivedate=2021-01-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106212609/https://www.wsls.com/news/virginia/2021/01/06/gov-northam-sending-virginia-national-guard-and-200-state-troopers-to-washington-dc/|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[马里兰州|马里兰州]]州长[[拉里·霍甘|拉里·霍甘]]也宣布将派出马里兰州州警和马里兰州国民警卫队。<ref name="Hogan1">{{cite news|last1=Pramuk|first1=Jacob|title=National Guard will head to the Capitol to tamp down pro-Trump insurrection|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2021/01/06/pentagon-has-not-approved-request-for-national-guard-to-come-to-capitol.html|access-date=2021-01-06|work=[[全國廣播公司商業頻道|全國廣播公司商業頻道]]|date=2021-01-06|language=en|archivedate=2021-01-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106212457/https://www.cnbc.com/2021/01/06/pentagon-has-not-approved-request-for-national-guard-to-come-to-capitol.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Maryland Troopers Heading To DC To Help Quell Unrest At US Capitol, Hogan Says|url=https://baltimore.cbslocal.com/2021/01/06/maryland-troopers-heading-to-dc-to-help-quell-protests-at-us-capitol-hogan-says/|accessdate=2021-01-06|date=2021-01-06|archivedate=2021-01-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106212532/https://baltimore.cbslocal.com/2021/01/06/maryland-troopers-heading-to-dc-to-help-quell-protests-at-us-capitol-hogan-says/|dead-url=no}}</ref>下午3点45分左右，代理国防部长[[克里斯托弗·米勒|克里斯托弗·米勒]]在征求副总统[[迈克·彭斯|彭斯]]、众议院议长[[南希·佩洛西|佩洛西]]、参议员多数党领袖[[米奇·麥康諾|麦康奈尔]]、参议院少数党领袖[[查克·舒默|舒默]]和众议院多数党领袖[[斯坦利·霍耶|霍耶]]的意见之后，決定自行指示国民警卫队和其他“额外的支持”应对骚乱{{fact|（此次總統異常行為造成無人指揮的法律漏洞）|time=2021-11-22}}。<ref>{{cite news|title=Trump supporters storm Capitol as McConnell warns of democracy 'death spiral'|url=https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/live/2021/jan/06/georgia-election-latest-news-senate-ossoff-warnock-democrats-republicans-trump-biden|access-date=2021-01-06|work=[[衛報|衛報]]|date=2021-01-06|archivedate=2021-01-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106230506/https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/live/2021/jan/06/georgia-election-latest-news-senate-ossoff-warnock-democrats-republicans-trump-biden|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Army deploys D.C. National Guard to Capitol, and F.B.I. mobilizes agents.|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/06/us/politics/national-guard-capitol-army.html|date=2021-01-06|first1=Helene|last1=Cooper|first2=Julian E.|last2=Barnes|first3=Eric|last3=Schmitt|first4=Jonathan|last4=Martin|via=NYTimes.com|access-date=2021-01-06|archivedate=2021-01-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106213727/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/06/us/politics/national-guard-capitol-army.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Statement by Acting Secretary Miller on Full Activation of D.C. National Guard|url=https://www.defense.gov/Newsroom/Releases/Release/Article/2464427/statement-by-acting-secretary-miller-on-full-activation-of-dc-national-guard/|accessdate=2021-01-07|work=[[美國國防部|美國國防部]]|language=en-US|archivedate=2021-01-07|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107070342/https://www.defense.gov/Newsroom/Releases/Release/Article/2464427/statement-by-acting-secretary-miller-on-full-activation-of-dc-national-guard/|dead-url=no}}</ref>当地时间下午5时许，陆军部长莱恩·麦卡锡（Ryan McCarthy）和[[克里斯托弗·米勒|米勒]]决定部署华盛顿特区国民警卫队全部1100人的兵力来平息暴力事件。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Cooper|first1=Helene|title=Army activates D.C. National Guard to deploy troops to the Capitol.|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/06/us/politics/national-guard-capitol-army.html|work=紐約時報|date=2021-01-06|access-date=2021-01-06|archivedate=2021-01-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106213727/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/06/us/politics/national-guard-capitol-army.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>因為統帥的軍隊調動權問題已來不及處理，最終部署的命令只好由副总统彭斯破例批准。<ref>{{cite web|title=Army deploys D.C. National Guard to Capitol, and F.B.I. mobilizes agents.|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/06/us/politics/national-guard-capitol-army.html?smid=tw-nytimes&smtyp=cur|accessdate=2021-01-06|date=2021-01-06|work=紐約時報|last1=Cooper|first1=Helene|display-authors=et al|archivedate=2021-01-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106235805/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/06/us/politics/national-guard-capitol-army.html?smid=tw-nytimes&smtyp=cur|dead-url=no}}</ref>据《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》报道，“不清楚”为什么批准部署的不是三軍領導特朗普。<ref>{{Cite news|last=Haberman|first=Maggie|last2=Cooper|first2=Helene|date=2021-01-07|title=Trump rebuffed initial requests to deploy the National Guard to the Capitol. Pence gave the go-ahead.|language=en-US|work=紐約時報|url=https://www.nytimes.com/live/2021/01/06/us/washington-dc-protests|access-date=2021-01-07|issn=0362-4331|archivedate=2021-01-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106202204/https://www.nytimes.com/live/2021/01/06/us/washington-dc-protests|dead-url=no}}</ref>

