==== 简易爆炸装置 ====
[[File:Jan_6_pipe_bomb.jpg|thumb]]
有兩個简易爆炸装置被發現放置在國會外的兩棟建築物中，於中午12:45在[[共和黨全國委員會|共和黨全國委員會]]办公室所在的大楼旁邊发现了一个疑似[[管状炸弹|管状炸弹]]的装置。<ref name="IED-CNN" />約半小時後，另一個裝有管狀炸彈的可疑包裹在[[民主黨全國委員會|民主黨全國委員會]]总部的草叢中被搜獲，發現炸彈的地點和鄰近建築物都被臨時疏散<ref name=":6">{{Cite news|last=Barrett|first=Devlin|last2=Dawsey|first2=Josh|date=2021-01-06|title=Suspected homemade bombs found near RNC and DNC headquarters|work=[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/dc-md-va/2021/01/06/dc-protests-trump-rally-live-updates/|access-date=2021-01-06|archivedate=2021-01-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106194011/https://www.washingtonpost.com/dc-md-va/2021/01/06/dc-protests-trump-rally-live-updates/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=ABC.Hazardous/><ref name=Seattle.Obscured>{{cite news|url=https://www.seattletimes.com/nation-world/nation-politics/discovery-of-pipe-bombs-in-dc-obscured-by-riot-at-capitol/|title=Discovery of pipe bombs in DC obscured by riot at Capitol|work=[[西雅圖時報|西雅圖時報]]|last=Balsamo|first=Michael|date=January 11, 2021|access-date=January 11, 2021|archivedate=2021-01-11|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111225042/https://www.seattletimes.com/nation-world/nation-politics/discovery-of-pipe-bombs-in-dc-obscured-by-riot-at-capitol/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。共和党全国委员会大楼和民主黨全國委員會总部离[[美國國會大廈|国会大厦]]只有几个街区。<ref>{{cite web|title=An explosive device is found at the R.N.C., and the D.N.C. is evacuated.|url=https://www.nytimes.com/live/2021/01/06/us/electoral-vote#pipe-bomb-rnc|author=Katie Benner, Maggie Haberman and Michael S. Schmidt|date=2021-01-06|newspaper=紐約時報|access-date=2021-01-06|archivedate=2021-01-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106201215/https://www.nytimes.com/live/2021/01/06/us/electoral-vote#pipe-bomb-rnc|dead-url=no}}</ref>1月6日下午，在共和党全国委员会大楼和国会大厦院内发现的装置都被拆弹小组安全引爆<ref name="IED-CNN" />。官方不确定这些装置是否处于工作状态<ref>{{Cite web|title=FBI says 2 suspicious devices found amid pro-Trump riots were rendered safe|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2021/01/06/fbi-says-it-is-investigating-suspicious-devices-in-washington.html|date=2021-01-06|last=Higgins|first=Tucker|language=en|access-date=2021-01-07|work=[[全國廣播公司商業頻道|全國廣播公司商業頻道]]|archivedate=2021-01-07|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107025805/https://www.cnbc.com/2021/01/06/fbi-says-it-is-investigating-suspicious-devices-in-washington.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但指出兩者的構造相似，都是約{{convert|1|foot|cm}}長和連接了計時器<ref name=Seattle.Obscured/>。[[聯邦調查局|聯邦調查局]]發布懷疑放置炸彈的疑犯的照片並懸紅五萬美元給提供情報者<ref name="ABC.Posts">{{cite news|url=https://abcnews.go.com/Politics/fbi-posts-photo-person-suspected-pipe-bombs-dnc/story?id=75126041|title=FBI posts photo of person who placed suspected pipe bombs outside DNC, RNC|work=[[ABC新聞|ABC新聞]]|last=Sanchez|first=Rosa|date=January 7, 2021|access-date=January 8, 2021|archivedate=2021-01-08|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108070426/https://abcnews.go.com/Politics/fbi-posts-photo-person-suspected-pipe-bombs-dnc/story?id=75126041|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在一枚炸弹安置的地點附近發現有一辆载有[[步枪|步枪]]和[[燃烧瓶|燃烧瓶]]的汽车，一人因此被捕<ref name=":6" />。华盛顿特区警察还报告称，发现了一个装有[[燃烧瓶|燃烧瓶]]的冷藏箱<ref name="DC-police-update">{{cite news |title=Over 50 people arrested, 14 officers injured and 4 deaths reported amid pro-Trump protests in DC |url=https://www.fox5dc.com/news/over-50-people-arrested-14-officers-injured-amid-pro-trump-protests-in-dc-police-say |work=福斯5華盛頓特區 |date=2021-01-06 |accessdate=2021-01-07 |archivedate=2021-01-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107065255/https://www.fox5dc.com/news/over-50-people-arrested-14-officers-injured-and-4-deaths-reported-amid-pro-trump-protests-in-dc |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==== 事后处理 ====
[[File:Riot_police_and_protester_outside_United_States_Capitol_at_evening_20210106.jpg|缩略图]]
警方继续试图将暴动者驅離国会大厦。抗议活动仍在继续，一些人则撤出了[[国会山|国会山]]地区。据报道，一些人对记者进行了言语和肢体攻击，攻击者诋毁媒体机构为“[[假新聞|假新聞]]”。<ref name="BBC-live">{{cite news|title=Violent pro-Trump mob storms US Capitol|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/live/election-us-2020-55558355|work=英國廣播公司新聞|language=en-gb|access-date=2021-01-06|archivedate=2021-01-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106232353/https://www.bbc.com/news/live/election-us-2020-55558355|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Capitol rioter to CNN: We could absolutely f***ing destroy you|url=https://www.cnn.com/2021/01/10/media/cnn-correspondent-capitol-reliable/index.html|accessdate=2021-01-11|last=Business|first=Alexis Benveniste|work=有線電視新聞網|archivedate=2021-01-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113080619/https://www.cnn.com/2021/01/10/media/cnn-correspondent-capitol-reliable/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

截至下午6:08，警方在当天的事件中逮捕了至少13人，并缴获了5支枪支。<ref name="wednesday-arrests-NYT2">{{Cite news|last=Steinhauer|first=Jennifer|date=2021-01-06|title=Police in Washington seize 5 guns and arrest at least 13 during violent Capitol protest.|language=en-US|work=紐約時報|url=https://www.nytimes.com/live/2021/01/06/us/washington-dc-protests|access-date=2021-01-06|issn=0362-4331|archivedate=2021-01-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106202204/https://www.nytimes.com/live/2021/01/06/us/washington-dc-protests|dead-url=no}}</ref>虽然市长鲍瑟实施了晚上6点的宵禁，但基本上被人们忽视了，数百名支持特朗普的示威者仍然留在国会山地区。<ref>{{Cite web|title=After Chaos, Insurrection And Death, Pro-Trump Rioters Defy D.C. Curfew|url=https://www.npr.org/sections/congress-electoral-college-tally-live-updates/2021/01/06/954218720/after-chaos-insurrection-and-death-pro-trump-rioters-defy-d-c-curfew|language=en|access-date=2021-01-07|work=[[全國公共廣播電台|全國公共廣播電台]]|archivedate=2021-01-07|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107032311/https://www.npr.org/sections/congress-electoral-college-tally-live-updates/2021/01/06/954218720/after-chaos-insurrection-and-death-pro-trump-rioters-defy-d-c-curfew|dead-url=no}}</ref>截至晚上10:30。又有47人因违反宵禁而被逮捕。<ref name="DC-police-update" />至少有6人因当天的事件而住院，其中包括一名执法人员。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Bredderman|first1=Blake Montgomery,Pilar Melendez,William|title=Woman Shot Dead as Mob Overran Capitol ID’ed as Air Force Vet|url=https://www.thedailybeast.com/one-woman-shot-six-hospitalized-as-trump-loving-mob-swarms-capitol|work=[[每日野獸|每日野獸]]|date=2021-01-06|language=en|accessdate=2021-01-07|archivedate=2021-01-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106210258/https://www.thedailybeast.com/one-woman-shot-six-hospitalized-as-trump-loving-mob-swarms-capitol|dead-url=no}}</ref>14名华盛顿特区警察局的警察受伤。4人死亡；1人在国会大厦被执法人员开枪打死，另外3人死于医疗紧急情况。<ref name="DC-police-update" />

1月6日晚，华盛顿特区国民警卫队的2700名士兵和弗吉尼亚国民警卫队的650名士兵将被派往华盛顿特区。<ref>{{Cite news|last=Schmitt|first=Eric|date=2021-01-06|title=The entire D.C. National Guard has been mobilized.|language=en-US|work=紐約時報|url=https://www.nytimes.com/live/2021/01/06/us/washington-dc-protests|access-date=2021-01-06|issn=0362-4331|archivedate=2021-01-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106202204/https://www.nytimes.com/live/2021/01/06/us/washington-dc-protests|dead-url=no}}</ref>1月6日晚，市长鲍瑟发布新的命令，将华盛顿特区的公共紧急状态延长15天，她在命令中写道，她预计一些人将“在就职典礼前继续进行暴力抗议活动”。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Levenson|first1=Michael|title=Washington, D.C. mayor issues order extending emergency for 15 days.|url=https://www.nytimes.com/live/2021/01/06/us/washington-dc-protests/washington-dc-mayor-issues-order-extending-emergency-for-15-days|access-date=2021-01-07|work=紐約時報|date=2021-01-07|archivedate=2021-01-07|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107052550/https://www.nytimes.com/live/2021/01/06/us/washington-dc-protests/washington-dc-mayor-issues-order-extending-emergency-for-15-days|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Citation|last=Bowser|first=Muriel|title=Mayor's Order 2021-003|date=2021-01-06|url=https://mayor.dc.gov/sites/default/files/dc/sites/mayormb/release_content/attachments/Mayor%27s%20Order%202021-003.pdf|accessdate=2021-01-07|archivedate=2021-01-07|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107052454/https://mayor.dc.gov/sites/default/files/dc/sites/mayormb/release_content/attachments/Mayor%27s%20Order%202021-003.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==== 国会恢复议程 ====
在清场后，参议院率先于1月6日晚8时复会恢复辩论，并简短谴责了示威群众入侵国会的行为。<ref>{{Cite web|title='Violence never wins': Senate reconvenes to continue Electoral College count after pro-Trump riot at Capitol|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/elections/2021/01/06/electoral-college-vote-stopped-unclear-when-resume-after-riot/6572441002/|accessdate=2021-01-07|last=Shesgreen|first=Joey Garrison and Deirdre|work=[[今日美國|今日美國]]|language=en-US|archivedate=2021-01-07|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107071026/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/elections/2021/01/06/electoral-college-vote-stopped-unclear-when-resume-after-riot/6572441002/|dead-url=no}}</ref>众议院议长[[南希·佩洛西|南希·佩洛西]]表示，国会大厦遇袭事件不会“阻止我们履行确认乔·拜登当选的责任”，她与其他众议院领袖、[[五角大楼|五角大楼]]、[[美国司法部|司法部]]和[[迈克·彭斯|迈克·彭斯]]协商后，决定当晚重新召开会议。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Congress will reconvene to certify Biden's Electoral College win|url=https://www.politico.com/news/2021/01/06/congress-confirms-bidens-win-trump-455253|accessdate=2021-01-07|work=[[政客_(媒體)|政客]]|archivedate=2021-01-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106211409/https://www.politico.com/news/2021/01/06/congress-confirms-bidens-win-trump-455253|dead-url=no}}</ref>最终，當地時間1月7日凌晨3時41分，国会联席会议确认了拜登当选。<ref>{{cite news |author1=邓仙来, 孙丁 |title=美国国会联席会议确认拜登当选总统 |url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2021-01/07/c_1126956954.htm |accessdate=2021-01-07 |agency=新华社 |date=2021-01-07 |language=zh-hans |archivedate=2021-01-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108131014/http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2021-01/07/c_1126956954.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 騷亂過後 ===
2021年1月7日晚上約9:30，早前在國會衝突中遇襲受傷的國會警員席克尼克（Brian D. Sicknick）證實傷重死亡。眾議院議長佩洛西要求國會大廈[[下半旗|下半旗]]致哀。副總統彭斯則向席克尼克的家人表示深切慰問，並形容席克尼克為保衛國會大廈的英雄<ref name=CNN.Sicknick>{{Cite news|date=2021-01-08|title=Capitol Police officer who died when mob stormed the Capitol was proud to serve his nation, family said|work=美國有線電視新聞網|language=en-US|url=https://www.cnn.com/2021/01/08/us/brian-sicknick-death/index.html|access-date=2021-01-09|archivedate=2021-01-12|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112105837/https://www.cnn.com/2021/01/08/us/brian-sicknick-death/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1月9日，佩洛西指示國會大廈外的國旗[[半旗|下降一半]]悼念席克尼克<ref name="nyt-2021-01-09-haberman-schmidt">{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/09/us/politics/flag-lowering-trump-sicknick.html|title=Trump has not lowered flags in honor of an officer who died from injuries sustained amid the riot.|work=紐約時報|date=2021-01-09|access-date=2021-01-09|first1=Maggie|last1=Haberman|first2=Michael S.|last2=Schmidt|archivedate=2021-01-10|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110180711/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/09/us/politics/flag-lowering-trump-sicknick.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，特朗普則下令1月13日将美国国旗半降<ref name=cnnews0111/>。

多個州份議會大樓提高警戒級別，以防示威者衝擊<ref name="Georgia">{{cite web|title=Georgia Secretary of State evacuates Georgia Capitol for safety, office closes|url=https://www.11alive.com/article/news/politics/atlanta-georgia-capitol-pro-trump-protest/85-bf35b7fb-0c47-4087-b218-d73240b2d80e|access-date=2021-01-06|work=[[WXIA-TV|WXIA-TV]]|archivedate=2021-01-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106212614/https://www.11alive.com/article/news/politics/atlanta-georgia-capitol-pro-trump-protest/85-bf35b7fb-0c47-4087-b218-d73240b2d80e|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Texas">{{cite web|title=Texas Capitol grounds in Austin closed as Trump supporters storm US Capitol|url=https://www.kvue.com/article/news/local/austin-rally-protest-march-for-trump/269-6df202da-cabb-43fe-b4f8-2a3bda77de92|access-date=2021-01-06|work=[[KVUE|KVUE]]|archivedate=2021-01-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106212616/https://www.kvue.com/article/news/local/austin-rally-protest-march-for-trump/269-6df202da-cabb-43fe-b4f8-2a3bda77de92|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美國各地有支援是次衝擊示威以及反對川普人士<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://abc7ny.com/anti-trump-protest-results-in-8-arrests-in-new-york-city/9429022/ |title=Anti-Trump protest at Trump Tower results in 8 arrests in New York City |work=WABC-TV |accessdate=2021-01-10 |archivedate=2021-01-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112150119/https://abc7ny.com/anti-trump-protest-results-in-8-arrests-in-new-york-city/9429022/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>進行各式各樣的示威。

海外亦有零星示威。例如日本時間1月6日晚上，即衝擊美國國會前數小時，日本[[東京都|東京都]]有約數百人聚集支持川普，並高舉[[美國國旗|美國國旗]]及日本[[旭日旗|旭日旗]]從[[日比谷|日比谷]]遊行至[[銀座|銀座]]，活動由新興宗教組織[[幸福科學|幸福科學]]背後支援<ref name=wapojapan>{{cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/2021/01/07/trump-qanon-stop-the-steal-japan/|title=Trump’s ‘stop the steal’ message finds an international audience among conspiracy theorists and suspected cults|date=2021-01-07|accessdate=2021-01-08|work=華盛頓郵報|last=Taylor|first=Adam|archivedate=2021-01-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113010400/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/2021/01/07/trump-qanon-stop-the-steal-japan/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1月10日，美国国会警察局证实，另一名曾在骚乱当天于国会内执勤的国会警员霍华德·莱本古德（Howard Liebengood）于9日下班时逝世。官方未公开莱本古德的具体死因；但据部分媒体报道，莱本古德是[[自杀|自杀]]身亡<ref name=cnnews0111>{{cite news |author1=陈孟统 |title=特朗普下令全美降半旗向在冲击国会事件中牺牲警员致哀 |url=https://www.chinanews.com/gj/2021/01-11/9383766.shtml |accessdate=2021-01-11 |agency=中国新闻社 |date=2021-01-11 |archivedate=2021-01-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112081611/https://www.chinanews.com/gj/2021/01-11/9383766.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="wp0110">{{cite news |author1=Allison Klein, Rebecca Tan |title=An off-duty U.S. Capitol Police officer has died; law enforcement officials cite suicide |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/public-safety/liebengood-capitol-police-death/2021/01/10/3a495b84-5357-11eb-a08b-f1381ef3d207_story.html |accessdate=2021-01-11 |work=華盛頓郵報 |date=2021-01-10 |archivedate=2021-01-13 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113072502/https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/public-safety/liebengood-capitol-police-death/2021/01/10/3a495b84-5357-11eb-a08b-f1381ef3d207_story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

