iden/index.html|work=有線電視新聞網|access-date=2021-01-06|archivedate=2021-01-07|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107025828/https://www.cnn.com/2021/01/06/politics/electoral-college-challenge-cathy-mcmorris-rodgers-biden/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>与她一起的还有参议员{{tsl|en|Kelly Loeffler|凯莉·洛夫勒}}、[[史蒂夫·戴恩斯|史蒂夫·戴恩斯]]、[[詹姆斯·蘭克福德|詹姆斯·蘭克福德]]、[[玛莎·布莱克本|玛莎·布莱克本]]、[[迈克·布劳恩|迈克·布劳恩]]和[[辛西婭·拉米斯|辛西婭·拉米斯]]，这些议员在目睹了闯入国会的特朗普支持者们制造的暴力事件后，都在反对选举人票的问题上改弦更张。<ref name="GOPreverse">{{cite news|last=LeBlanc|first=Paul|date=2021-01-06|title=US Capitol breach prompts host of GOP lawmakers to decide against challenging Biden's win|url=https://www.cnn.com/2021/01/06/politics/electoral-college-challenge-cathy-mcmorris-rodgers-biden/index.html|work=有線電視新聞網|access-date=2021-01-07|archivedate=2021-01-07|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107025828/https://www.cnn.com/2021/01/06/politics/electoral-college-challenge-cathy-mcmorris-rodgers-biden/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>犹他州参议员[[米特·羅姆尼|米特·羅姆尼]]表示，“今天在国会大厦发生的事情是一场由美国总统煽动的暴乱，是对我们的民主进行前所未有的攻击的一部分”。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Kelly|first1=Caroline|last2=Robertson|first2=Nicky|date=2021-01-06|title=Romney: 'What happened here today was an insurrection, incited by the President'|url=https://www.cnn.com/2021/01/06/politics/romney-trump-insurrection-capitol/index.html|work=有線電視新聞網|access-date=2020-01-06|archivedate=2021-01-07|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107025702/https://www.cnn.com/2021/01/06/politics/romney-trump-insurrection-capitol/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

