1月8日，美國眾議院議長佩洛西去信全體民主黨眾議員，表示她與[[美軍參謀長聯席會議|美軍參謀長聯席會議]]主席[[馬克·米利|馬克·米利]]通電話，商討預防措施以防止「精神不穩定」的特朗普運用總統的權力去發動[[核戰|核軍事攻擊]]。<ref>{{Cite news|date=2021-01-08|title=佩洛西： 擔心特朗普可能下令發動核攻擊|work=[[法國國際廣播電台|法國國際廣播電台]]|url=https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E7%BE%8E%E6%B4%B2/20210108-%E4%BD%A9%E6%B4%9B%E8%A5%BF-%E6%93%94%E5%BF%83%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%8B%E4%BB%A4%E7%99%BC%E5%8B%95%E6%A0%B8%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A|access-date=2021-01-09|archivedate=2021-01-11|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111092630/https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E7%BE%8E%E6%B4%B2/20210108-%E4%BD%A9%E6%B4%9B%E8%A5%BF-%E6%93%94%E5%BF%83%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%8B%E4%BB%A4%E7%99%BC%E5%8B%95%E6%A0%B8%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|date=2021-01-09|title=佩洛西指特朗普失常　促限制使用核武權力|work=[[東方日報|東方日報]]|url=https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/intnews/20210109/bkn-20210109012616825-0109_00992_001.html|access-date=2021-01-09|archivedate=2021-01-11|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111110250/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/intnews/20210109/bkn-20210109012616825-0109_00992_001.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>國防部亦表示特朗普仍為三軍總司令，軍方一定會執行他的合法命令，他們無法將特朗普從指揮系統中除名，否則這就是[[政變|政變]]<ref>{{cite news |last1=Sanger |first1=David E. |last2=Schmitt |first2=Eric |title=Pelosi Pressed Pentagon on Safeguards to Prevent Trump From Ordering Military Action |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/08/us/politics/trump-pelosi-nuclear-military.html |accessdate=2021-01-12 |work=紐約時報 |date=2021-01-08 |language=en |archivedate=2021-01-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112042141/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/08/us/politics/trump-pelosi-nuclear-military.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同日，佩洛西宣佈國會降半旗為此次事件中的遇難警察默哀<ref>{{cite news |title=美国国会设置铁栅栏加强安保 降半旗致哀死难警察 |url=http://www.chinaqw.com/m/yw/hd/2021/0109/8906.shtml |accessdate=2021-01-09 |archivedate=2021-01-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114195855/http://www.chinaqw.com/m/yw/hd/2021/0109/8906.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

1月9日，[[美國有線新聞網絡|美國有線新聞網絡]]引述知情人士報道，副總統彭斯不排除會動用憲法第25條修正案，但彭斯團隊擔心任何試圖迫使特朗普下台的舉動都會招來特朗普更過火的行動，可能令美國受威脅，而引用第25條修正案只是當中的選項之一。另一方面，眾議院民主黨議員宣布會於周一（1月11日）動議彈劾特朗普，截至1月9日晚上已獲得190名議員支持。有關動議文本將國會山莊騷亂歸咎於特朗普，指摘他「嚴重危及美國及其政府機構安全，威脅民主制度的健全，阻撓權力和平交接，破壞三權分立」。<ref>{{Cite news|date=2021-01-10|title=民主黨周一動議彈劾特朗普　傳彭斯保留罷免選項|work=[[東方日報|東方日報]]|url=https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/intnews/20210110/bkn-20210110120422015-0110_00992_001.html|access-date=2021-01-11|archivedate=2021-01-11|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111131430/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/intnews/20210110/bkn-20210110120422015-0110_00992_001.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|date=2021-01-10|title=美媒︰彭斯不排除動用憲法修正案罷免特朗普|work=[[明報|明報]]|url=https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20210110/s00005/1610267171942/%e7%be%8e%e5%aa%92-%e5%bd%ad%e6%96%af%e4%b8%8d%e6%8e%92%e9%99%a4%e5%8b%95%e7%94%a8%e6%86%b2%e6%b3%95%e4%bf%ae%e6%ad%a3%e6%a1%88%e7%bd%b7%e5%85%8d%e7%89%b9%e6%9c%97%e6%99%ae|access-date=2021-01-11|archivedate=2021-01-10|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110083809/https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20210110/s00005/1610267171942/%e7%be%8e%e5%aa%92-%e5%bd%ad%e6%96%af%e4%b8%8d%e6%8e%92%e9%99%a4%e5%8b%95%e7%94%a8%e6%86%b2%e6%b3%95%e4%bf%ae%e6%ad%a3%e6%a1%88%e7%bd%b7%e5%85%8d%e7%89%b9%e6%9c%97%e6%99%ae|dead-url=no}}</ref>1月10日，众议院议长南希·佩洛西要求副总统迈克·彭斯要求根据相关宪法修正案罢免总统唐纳德·特朗普，否则众议院将启动弹劾程序<ref>{{cite news |title=佩洛西推动弹劾特朗普 先给彭斯下通牒 |url=http://news.21cn.com/hot/int/a/2021/0111/16/49344979.shtml |accessdate=2021-01-11 |archivedate=2021-01-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111154128/http://news.21cn.com/hot/int/a/2021/0111/16/49344979.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

1月12日，[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]报导，参议院多数党领袖[[米奇·麥康諾|米奇·麥康諾]]对弹劾计划表示“满意”（pleased），同时认为弹劾的做法会让把特朗普从共和党驱逐出去的行为更加容易<ref>{{Cite news|title=McConnell is said to be pleased about impeachment, believing it will be easier to purge Trump from the G.O.P.|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/12/us/mitch-mcconnell-trump-impeachment.html|newspaper=紐約時報|date=2021-01-12|accessdate=2021-01-12|issn=0362-4331|language=en-US|first=Jonathan|last=Martin|first2=Maggie|last2=Haberman|archivedate=2021-01-12|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112234938/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/12/us/mitch-mcconnell-trump-impeachment.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同日，美国[[美国众议院|众议院]]的排名第三的共和党领导人（third-ranking GOP leader），也是共和党党团的领导人[[利茲·切尼|利茲·切尼]]说，她会支持弹劾<ref>{{Cite web|title=Rep. Liz Cheney backs Trump impeachment as some Republicans move against the president|url=https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/congress/house-set-vote-resolution-calling-pence-invoke-25th-amendment-n1253873|accessdate=2021-01-12|work=[[NBC新聞|NBC新聞]]|language=en|archivedate=2021-01-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113031021/https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/congress/house-set-vote-resolution-calling-pence-invoke-25th-amendment-n1253873|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在此之后，众议院共和党领导人表示他们不会要求共和党议员反对弹劾<ref>{{Cite web|title=House GOP Leaders Won’t Lobby Caucus to Oppose Impeachment|url=https://www.nationalreview.com/news/house-gop-leaders-wont-lobby-caucus-to-oppose-impeachment/|accessdate=2021-01-13|date=2021-01-12|work=[[國家評論|國家評論]]|language=en-US|archivedate=2021-01-14|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114195843/https://www.nationalreview.com/news/house-gop-leaders-wont-lobby-caucus-to-oppose-impeachment/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同日，众议院通过H.R. 21，要求彭斯动用第25条修正案成为代理总统。在彭斯拒绝动用修正案的当日晚上，佩洛西提名了弹劾案的管理员（impeachment managers）<ref>{{Cite web|title=Pelosi Names Impeachment Managers|url=https://www.speaker.gov/newsroom/11221-0|accessdate=2021-01-13|date=2021-01-12|work=南希·佩洛西|language=en|archivedate=2021-01-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113065707/https://www.speaker.gov/newsroom/11221-0|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1月13日，众议院启动弹劾程序。在长达两个小时的辩论之后，有十名共和党众议员决定支持弹劾<ref>{{Cite web|title=These House Republicans say they will vote to impeach Trump|url=https://www.cbsnews.com/news/house-republicans-weigh-voting-to-impeach-trump/|accessdate=2021-01-13|work=[[CBS新聞|CBS新聞]]|language=en-US|archivedate=2021-01-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113082539/https://www.cbsnews.com/news/house-republicans-weigh-voting-to-impeach-trump/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。随后，弹劾议案以232-197的比例通过，特朗普成为美国历史上第一位被弹劾两次的总统<ref>{{Cite news|title=Live Updates: The House, With Some G.O.P. Support, Votes to Impeach Trump a Historic Second Time|url=https://www.nytimes.com/live/2021/01/13/us/trump-impeachment|newspaper=紐約時報|date=2021-01-13|accessdate=2021-01-13|issn=0362-4331|language=en-US|first=Nicholas|last=Fandos|archivedate=2021-01-14|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114144704/https://www.nytimes.com/live/2021/01/13/us/trump-impeachment|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同日，参议院多数党领袖[[米奇·麥康諾|米奇·麥康諾]]拒绝提早召集参议院来审判特朗普<ref>{{Cite web|title=McConnell won't agree to reconvene Senate early for impeachment trial|url=https://thehill.com/homenews/senate/534053-mcconnell-wont-agree-to-reconvene-senate-early-for-impeachment-trial|accessdate=2021-01-13|date=2021-01-13|last=Zilbermints|first=Regina|work=[[國會山報|國會山報]]|language=en|archivedate=2021-01-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113193717/https://thehill.com/homenews/senate/534053-mcconnell-wont-agree-to-reconvene-senate-early-for-impeachment-trial|dead-url=no}}</ref>，这代表参议院有极大的可能性会在特朗普任期结束之后才审判特朗普的弹劾案。拜登上任后，民主党控制的参议院决定在2月9日开始审判<ref>{{Cite web|title=Senate impeachment trial arguments to start February 9|url=https://www.cnn.com/2021/01/22/politics/impeachment-articles-schumer/index.html|accessdate=2021-02-05|last=CNN|first=Jeremy Herb, Manu Raju and Clare Foran|work=CNN|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308233846/https://www.cnn.com/2021/01/22/politics/impeachment-articles-schumer/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2月9日，弹劾案的审判程序正式在由[[美國參議院臨時議長|参议院临时议长]][[派屈克·萊希|派屈克·莱希]]主持参议院开始。在2月13日，参议院经过五天的审判程序后，57名参议员投票认为特朗普有罪、43名认为无罪。因“有罪”票数未达到在场参议员的三分之二（也就是67票），临时议长宣布特朗普无罪<ref>{{Cite web|title=Former President Donald Trump acquitted in 2nd impeachment trial|url=https://abcnews.go.com/Politics/president-donald-trump-acquitted/story?id=75853994|accessdate=2021-02-17|last=News|first=A. B. C.|work=ABC News|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210304130442/https://abcnews.go.com/Politics/president-donald-trump-acquitted/story?id=75853994|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

5月14日，[[美国众议院|美国众议院]]国土安全委员会的两名分属民主党和共和党的成员宣布组建一个委员会，对冲击国会大厦的叛乱事件展开两党合作调查<ref>{{Cite web|title=美两党议员同意成立委员会调查冲击国会大厦事件|url=https://www.voachinese.com/a/agreement-reached-for-bipartisan-probe-into-us-capitol-riot-20210514/5891203.html|work=美国之音|date=2021年5月15日|access-date=2021年5月15日|archive-date=2021年5月21日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210521193442/https://www.voachinese.com/a/agreement-reached-for-bipartisan-probe-into-us-capitol-riot-20210514/5891203.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。6月8日，[[美国国会参议院|美国国会参议院]]發佈国会大厦遭冲击事件的调查报告，報告认为联邦情报机构、执法机构的共同失误导致了国会大厦遭冲击事件的发生<ref>{{cite news |title=美参议院发布1月6日国会骚乱事件调查报告 |url=http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2021/06-09/9495895.shtml |accessdate=2021-06-09 |archive-date=2021-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210609165844/http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2021/06-09/9495895.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。6月30日，美国众议院批准成立专门委员会调查1月6日冲击国会大厦骚乱的决议案<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://sputniknews.cn/politics/202107011033990565/|title=美国众议院批准成立专门委员会调查冲击国会大厦案|publisher=俄罗斯卫星通讯社|date=2021-07-01|accessdate=2021-07-01|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210701082232/https://sputniknews.cn/politics/202107011033990565/|archivedate=2021-07-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

