O約翰·馬澤在1月10日接受[[霍士新聞頻道|霍士新聞]]訪問時表示，所有供應商包括短信服務，電郵服務等，還有律師顧問都在同一天切断了与Parler的关系<ref>{{cite news|author1=Jay Peters|title=Parler CEO says even his lawyers are abandoning him|url=https://www.theverge.com/2021/1/10/22223956/parler-ceo-john-matze-lawyers-vendors-abandoning|accessdate=2021-01-11|work=[[The_Verge|The Verge]]|date=2021-01-10|language=en|archivedate=2021-01-12|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112023404/https://www.theverge.com/2021/1/10/22223956/parler-ceo-john-matze-lawyers-vendors-abandoning|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在1月11日，Parler网站已经无法连接上<ref>{{cite news |title=遭科技巨頭封殺 保守派社交平台Parler已斷線 |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202101110228.aspx |accessdate=2021-01-13 |work=[[中央社通訊社|中央社通訊社]] |language=zh-tw |archivedate=2021-01-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111234423/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202101110228.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

